snippet.title: Henri’s Secret 2 | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Finding her path isn't easy for Lyla... And living a love story with a star is even harder! While she and Henri are finally together, secret-free, their relationship will be put to the test. Between the media, the international tours, and a certain new celebrity's growing interest for Jay... 

Will their love survive the life of a star?
